CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 25, 2005

[Cite as 04/25/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1887.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2005-0190. Wears v. Motorists Mut. Ins. Co.

Summit App. No. 22027, 2004-Ohio-6734 and 2005-Ohio-341. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
